---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Mobile Apps Development">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>iOS, Android &amp; Windows Mobile Development</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies is a pioneer in mobile app development for iPad, iPhone, Android, Blackberry and Windows platforms. Our developers have years of experience, from conventional SMS alerts to fully integrated solutions, all delivered faster through offshore cost advantages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-apple"></i></div>
            <h5>iOS Apps</h5>
            <p>GPS-based iPhone applications, in-app shopping, file sharing for iPad and feature-rich iOS apps tailored to your business needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-android"></i></div>
            <h5>Android Apps</h5>
            <p>Native Android applications with seamless performance across the full range of Android devices and screen sizes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-windows"></i></div>
            <h5>Windows Mobile</h5>
            <p>Windows mobile app development with consistent experience across all screen sizes and Windows device categories.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-truck"></i></div>
            <h5>Logistics &amp; Inventory</h5>
            <p>Track and verify inventory, logistics and warehouse management in real time through purpose-built mobile applications.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-users"></i></div>
            <h5>Workforce Management</h5>
            <p>Mobile workforce management apps and CRM-based solutions to keep your teams connected and productive in the field.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-refresh"></i></div>
            <h5>Sales Force Automation</h5>
            <p>Sales force automation and order status tracking apps that give your sales team real-time data wherever they are.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
